{"type": "article", "id": 16910, "title": "Clamp Ring", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-02T06:50:12Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 9, "praise_count": 71, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702125736RS6pTst0cvX4P3iN.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n\t这些饰品来自台湾的工作室 Drilling Lab，直接用了螺丝钉和不锈钢，有浓厚的工业感。饰品包括戒指，耳钉和手链，都是用低过敏的医疗级不锈钢。螺丝钉是用来调整松紧度，耳钉就是通过调整螺丝钉的距离以戴在耳朵上，很有手感。戒指另有一款直接套在手上，用镀金和黑色相称，很有个性。整个系列都偏中性，男女皆可，简单而率性，<a href=\"http://www.duo.com.tw/brand.php?id=55&amp;partner=DAMANWOO2015\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144148RAvTLZgxEbGkV705.jpg\" width=\"650\" height=\"384\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.59076923\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144149bBgj42eWDChYywXf.jpg\" width=\"650\" height=\"384\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.59076923\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144149WHYtSPBXcuKV1R0f.jpg\" width=\"650\" height=\"433\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66615385\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144150cbnt1JoUj5P2pVgr.jpg\" width=\"650\" height=\"476\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.73230769\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261441503AwuZB8W27JhfXgU.jpg\" width=\"650\" height=\"434\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66769231\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}